Use of proceeds from the previous financing
As of the Latest Practicable Date, approximately 40% of the previous financing proceeds had been utilized. Such proceeds were
utilized for the research and development, capital expenditures and general working capital needs of MiniMax. The Company
plans to utilize the remaining 60% proceeds from the previous financing for cloud services procurement related to training and
inferencing, human resources matters and marketing activities.
